Title: More Leverage on Stuff
---
This is the wolf whistle refrain, for such pizzazz and cleverness as that
 last ditty possessed deserves an encore.
Besides this being a very practical truth, we have a significant furthermore,
 which is： Anyone who seriously contemplates this, meditates upon it for
 at least nine minutes ...
could discover they got more leverage on stuff they want to have leverage over.
Sounds useful, the above. So here goes again, that deep preliminary thought：
If God just stopped controlling Himself and gave us all a big WW-that would
 about cover it, maybe forever and ever and ever.
